Lazy-Loading
------------
* provide less loading for high traffic pages.
* /* * syntax :- ng g module module-name --route module-name --module app.module */

JSON SERVER
============
1. Install server
    npm i  --save json-server 
2.  Run server in file location
    syntax :- npx json-server --watch db.json --port 3000      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
pipe creation
-------------
syntax :- ng g pipe pipename

Behaviour subjects
------------------
to share data between modules.
rxjs(reactive extension for js) library of behaviour subject.
rxjs is used to handle async implementaion in angular.
it's aynchrous data.

activated route in angular
--------------------------
* used to access data from url(access params)
* activatedRouter - class
* params() - method
* it's a asynchronous method.